text: Meziboří () is a town in Most District in the Ústí nad Labem Region of the Czech Republic. == Twin towns == Meziboří is twinned with: * Sayda, Germany * Sogliano al Rubicone, Italy == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Towns in the Czech Republic Category:Ústí nad Labem Region
